on why they've appeared here.

05:35.001 --> 05:37.834
The first is that they escaped
from a zoo vehicle.

05:38.004 --> 05:39.995
The second is that
they're abandoned pets.

05:40.131 --> 05:41.731
The third is that
they're crows that have

05:41.800 --> 05:43.440
