06:37.355 --> 06:41.189
Aoyama, what's so fun
about writing all that up?

06:41.443 --> 06:44.355
We don't think that penguins in
and of themselves are abnormal.

06:44.529 --> 06:46.190
We think it's strange
that penguins

06:46.364 --> 06:47.649
have appeared in the suburbs.

06:47.782 --> 06:48.612
What?

06:48.783 --> 06:49.397
