08:25.213 --> 08:26.213
Suzuki.

08:26.673 --> 08:27.788
What do you want?

08:28.216 --> 08:32.049
You have that disease, as well?
I can tell by looking at you.

08:32.761 --> 08:33.922
What disease?

08:34.222 --> 08:37.009
You don't know? It's called
stanislaw's syndrome.

08:37.308 --> 08:38.592
It's a terrifying disease where

08:38.727 --> 08:40.058
all your teeth have
to be pulled.

08:40.562 --> 08:42.644
I've never heard of that.

08:42.938 --> 08:46.773
My mom only said I was getting
my wisdom teeth out...

08:47.861 --> 08:49.772
A mother wouldn't
tell their kid they're

08:49.946 --> 08:51.937
getting all their teeth pulled.
Too scary.

08:52.323 --> 08:54.359
Slowly but surely, all your
teeth will be pulled.

08:54.534 --> 08:55.614
That's what happened to me.

08:56.202 --> 08:58.818
But I think you have a right

08:58.997 --> 09:00.862
to know what's going
to happen to you.

09:01.583 --> 09:02.618
Seriously?

09:02.959 --> 09:04.745
The only way to stop
the spread of the

09:04.919 --> 09:06.625
disease is to pull
all of your teeth.

09:07.047 --> 09:09.379
If you don't, the bacteria
will spread,

09:09.549 --> 09:11.164
and your face will swell up.

09:11.593 --> 09:13.254
These mushroom-looking
things will start

09:13.428 --> 09:14.964
growing from the cracks
in your teeth.

09:15.180 --> 09:16.180
And after much pain,

09:16.723 --> 09:18.088
you'll die.

09:18.975 --> 09:20.715
Suzuki!

09:22.937 --> 09:24.973
In order to prevent that
from happening,

09:25.148 --> 09:26.638
the dentist will put you under,

09:26.816 --> 09:28.352
and slowly remove your teeth.

09:28.651 --> 09:32.815
But it's okay. You'll only be
in pain for a month.

09:33.114 --> 09:34.570
