You're trying to trick me!

10:08.149 --> 10:09.685
Young man.

10:11.277 --> 10:14.861
Why did you say that to suzuki?
Don't you feel bad for him?

10:15.031 --> 10:16.646
I feel bad for uchida.

10:16.908 --> 10:18.148
Who's uchida?

10:18.326 --> 10:21.318
This is not your problem.
You don't need to know.

10:22.163 --> 10:25.701
You baby. Guess you learned
how to dodge questions.

10:28.419 --> 10:29.955
Silly brat.

10:40.056 --> 10:42.342
This lady is a woman
who I've gotten

10:42.517 --> 10:44.257
to know here at the dentist.

10:44.811 --> 10:45.550
Hey there.

10:45.728 --> 10:49.516
Sorry, I'm teaching
this kid a lesson.

10:58.074 --> 11:01.032
I might have done something
a little immature.

11:01.202 --> 11:02.817
Well, you're still a kid.

11:02.996 --> 11:05.829
Suzuki was being mean to uchida.

11:05.999 --> 11:08.957
But uchida didn't really
ask me to get him back.

11:09.127 --> 11:11.368
So, I don't really
have the right to

11:11.546 --> 11:13.958
punish suzuki for what
he did to uchida.

11:14.132 --> 11:16.498
I should have talked
to uchida first,

11:16.676 --> 11:17.836
at the bare minimum.

11:18.011 --> 11:20.093
You've sure got a lot going on.

11:23.308 --> 11:24.844
Oh, look at this.

11:25.310 --> 11:27.175
Penguins are mysterious,
aren't they?

11:27.353 --> 11:29.093
Who knows what's going
on with them?

11:29.480 --> 11:32.222
Do you know about what
happened this morning?

11:32.692 --> 11:35.058
I heard. Even more
mysterious, huh?

11:35.945 --> 11:38.231
I love penguins.

11:38.406 --> 11:41.113
All right.
I'm going to take this.

11:41.993 --> 11:44.200
