12:37.590 --> 12:41.299
Good name.

12:41.844 --> 12:44.256
They really took me by surprise.

12:55.692 --> 12:57.899
I didn't think one of them
would come running out.

13:06.619 --> 13:09.156
I couldn't believe it.

13:46.701 --> 13:49.443
Young man,
look at the chess board.

13:49.871 --> 13:50.871
I am.

