19:47.061 --> 19:48.767
I'm going to punish you.

19:49.271 --> 19:50.886
Both of you.

19:51.190 --> 19:53.431
No, we're busy.

19:53.943 --> 19:55.558
Hey, you!

20:08.165 --> 20:09.165
Sorry!

20:09.291 --> 20:11.077
