22:23.676 --> 22:26.668
I wanted to take a bus,
but I was tired and fell asleep.

22:26.846 --> 22:27.846
Happens sometimes.

22:28.264 --> 22:29.674
Want me to pull that out?

22:29.849 --> 22:32.465
I'm fine.
I'll get it out myself.

22:32.643 --> 22:35.180
I'll do it nice for ya.
It'll be an experiment.

22:35.354 --> 22:37.015
I see. I like experiments.

22:38.899 --> 22:40.355
Let's see...

22:40.776 --> 22:42.858
Stay nice and still...

22:45.739 --> 22:48.105
Now, young man.
I'll pull this string,

22:48.284 --> 22:50.616
and we'll see if your
tooth comes out.

22:51.328 --> 22:52.328
Okay...

23:02.506 --> 23:03.506
Hey!

23:03.966 --> 23:07.550
I'm not scared.
My body's moving on its own.

23:09.430 --> 23:10.510
I know.

23:11.974 --> 23:13.714
I have a good idea.

23:13.893 --> 23:15.599
Watch closely.

23:16.604 --> 23:17.719
There we go!

23:21.400 --> 23:22.560
I thought there

23:23.193 --> 23:24.683
was no way that

23:25.154 --> 23:26.610
this would get
my tooth out, but...

23:56.685 --> 23:57.685
